{"tid":1336001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日蘋果頭版","createTime":"2019-07-20T17:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T18:34:12.000Z","uid":24345,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c45cde28d2ec03ce768af521e77c178e13e130d","tid":1336001,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXA9JND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXA9JND.png&h=c54b91a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【A1頭條】屯門、九龍、上水、沙田，潮水一樣的反送中反暴政運動，今天又回到港島。民陣發起今日大遊行，原定由維園走到中環，但被警方限制提前在灣仔結束。民陣提出上訴，但警方稱有情報顯示金鐘發生暴力衝擊風險極高，結果遊行只獲延長三小時至晚上11時59分，終點維持原判在灣仔修頓一帶。民陣指出，大量遊行人士無法迅速散去，將和灣仔會展的書展人潮爭路，離警察總部又只隔兩條街，若群眾因此失控，警方需負最大責任。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨2點半登入蘋果日報網站/動新聞app，即可閱覽最新日報內容。<br />\n==============<br />\n《蘋果動新聞》只限升級壹會員閱覽<br />\n🍎 新聞有價，立即$3訂閱：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Itz1ZW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Itz1ZW&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=a4cb288e\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Itz1ZW</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a5c2b2a6dbe206a4a17a3a06fba52c64f488382","tid":1336001,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"真係幫到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1a23122cf72a4498f569b6027ee72e97a42037","tid":1336001,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若群眾因此失控，警方需負最大責任</span></span>"},{"pid":"22b0cbd80dd22084f81e87f6d6e8f5b9460a4e3f","tid":1336001,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HONGKONGERS！ASSEMBLE！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=